.Dd March 28, 2026
.Dt GALE 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm gale
.Nd isolated package management for developers
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Ar command
.Op Ar args ...
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
installs CLI tools and runtimes into versioned,
isolated directories.
Each version occupies its own path in the store.
Nothing conflicts.
.Pp
Projects declare dependencies in
.Pa gale.toml ,
pinning exact versions.
.Cm sync
installs those versions.
.Cm update
bumps them.
A lockfile
.Pq Pa gale.lock
records SHA256 hashes for verification.
.Pp
Prebuilt binaries are pulled from GHCR when available.
Otherwise packages build from source.
Per-project environments activate on
.Xr cd 1
via
.Xr direnv 1 .
.Sh COMMANDS
.Ss Package Management
.Bl -tag -width "create-recipe" -compact
.It Cm install Ar pkg Ns Op @ Ns Ar ver
Install a package.
Fetches the latest version, or a specific version
with
.Ar @ver .
.It Cm remove Ar pkg
Remove a package from the store and config.
.It Cm add Ar pkg Ns Op @ Ns Ar ver ...
Add packages to
.Pa gale.toml
without installing.
.It Cm sync
Install all packages at the versions pinned in
.Pa gale.toml .
Verifies SHA256 against
.Pa gale.lock .
.It Cm update Op Ar pkg Ns Op @ Ns Ar ver ...
Update packages to the latest version, or to a
specific version with
.Ar @ver .
Without arguments, updates all packages.
.It Cm list
List packages in
.Pa gale.toml .
.It Cm gc
Remove unused package versions from the store.
.El
.Ss Inspection
.Bl -tag -width "create-recipe" -compact
.It Cm which Ar binary
Show which package provides a binary and its
store path.
.It Cm outdated
Show packages with newer versions available.
.It Cm diff
Show what
.Cm sync
would change.
.It Cm doctor
Check the installation for problems.
.It Cm search Ar query
Search for packages by name or description.
.El
.Ss Project Environment
.Bl -tag -width "create-recipe" -compact
.It Cm env
Print
.Ev PATH
export for the current scope.
.It Cm init
Create
.Pa gale.toml
and
.Pa .envrc
for a project.
.It Cm shell
Open a shell with the project environment.
.It Cm run Ar cmd
Run a command in the project environment.
.It Cm hook direnv
Print
.Fn use_gale
function for direnvrc.
.El
.Ss Recipe Development
.Bl -tag -width "create-recipe" -compact
.It Cm build Ar recipe.toml
Build a recipe from source.
.It Cm lint Ar recipe.toml ...
Validate recipe files.
.It Cm import homebrew Ar name
Import a Homebrew formula as a recipe.
.El
.Sh FLAGS
.Bl -tag -width "--no-color" -compact
.It Fl -local
Resolve recipes from a sibling
.Pa gale-recipes
directory.
Available on
.Cm install , sync , update , build , add .
.It Fl -source Ar dir
Build from a local source directory.
Version detected from
.Xr git-describe 1 ,
formatted as semver.
.It Fl -git
Clone and build from the git repository HEAD.
.It Fl -recipe Ar file
Use a specific recipe TOML file.
.It Fl g , -global
Write to the global config.
.It Fl p , -project
Write to the project config.
.It Fl -no-color
Disable colored output.
Respects
.Ev NO_COLOR .
.El
.Sh BUILD ENVIRONMENT
Build steps run in a clean shell.
These variables are set:
.Bl -tag -width "DYLD_FALLBACK_LIBRARY_PATH"
.It Ev PREFIX
Install destination directory.
.It Ev VERSION
The recipe's package version.
.It Ev JOBS
CPU count for parallel make.
.It Ev OS
Operating system
.Pq e.g., Dq darwin , Dq linux .
.It Ev ARCH
Architecture
.Pq e.g., Dq arm64 , Dq amd64 .
.It Ev PLATFORM
OS and architecture joined
.Pq e.g., Dq darwin-arm64 .
.It Ev LIBRARY_PATH
Library directories from build dependencies.
.It Ev C_INCLUDE_PATH
Header directories from build dependencies.
.It Ev PKG_CONFIG_PATH
Pkg-config directories from build dependencies.
.It Ev LD_LIBRARY_PATH
Dynamic linker path (Linux only).
.It Ev DYLD_FALLBACK_LIBRARY_PATH
Dynamic linker fallback path (macOS only).
.El
.Sh ENVIRONMENT
.Bl -tag -width "NO_COLOR"
.It Ev PATH
Add
.Pa ~/.gale/current/bin
for globally installed packages.
.It Ev NO_COLOR
Disables colored output when set.
.El
.Sh FILES
.Bl -tag -width "~/.gale/gale.toml"
.It Pa ~/.gale/gale.toml
Global package declarations.
.It Pa ~/.gale/config.toml
Application settings.
.It Pa ~/.gale/pkg/
Package store.
One directory per package per version.
.It Pa ~/.gale/current/
Symlink to the active generation.
.It Pa gale.toml
Project package declarations.
.It Pa gale.lock
Lockfile with version and SHA256 per package.
.It Pa .envrc
Direnv integration, created by
.Cm init .
.El
.Sh EXIT STATUS
.Ex -std
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr direnv 1 ,
.Xr git-describe 1
